longBusinessSummary: JB&ZJMY Holding Company, Inc. focuses on developing electrical cars and their support systems. The company was formerly known as Dolat Ventures, Inc. and changed its name to JB&ZJMY Holding Company, Inc. in October 2017. JB&ZJMY Holding Company, Inc. is based in Beijing, China.
